      <title>从写作到发布：Hexo 博客全流程实战</title>
      <link href="/2026/01/06/hexo-blog-workflow/"/>
      <url>/2026/01/06/hexo-blog-workflow/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>这篇记录我自己的博客工作流：从写一篇文章，到本地预览，再推送到 GitHub Pages。命令行一步步列清楚，照着做就能跑通。</p><h2 id="1-新建与书写"><a href="#1-新建与书写" class="headerlink" title="1. 新建与书写"></a>1. 新建与书写</h2><ol><li><p>新建文章（自动生成 Front Matter）：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new <span class="string">&quot;你的文章标题&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>默认会在 <code>source/_posts/</code> 下生成一个同名 Markdown。建议在 Front Matter 填上 <code>tags</code>、<code>categories</code>、<code>date</code> 方便归档。</p></li><li><p>写作时的常见小技巧：</p></li></ol><ul><li>图片放 <code>source/img/</code>，文章里引用 <code>/img/xxx.jpg</code>。</li><li>代码块用三反引号围住，注明语言更易高亮。</li><li>草稿模式可先放 <code>source/_drafts/</code>，预览时加 <code>hexo server --draft</code>。</li></ul><h2 id="2-本地预览检查"><a href="#2-本地预览检查" class="headerlink" title="2. 本地预览检查"></a>2. 本地预览检查</h2><p>先清再生成，保证产物干净：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pnpm run clean</span><br><span class="line">pnpm run build   <span class="comment"># 等价 hexo generate</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动本地预览（端口占用就换号，如 4002）：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pnpm <span class="built_in">exec</span> hexo server -p 4002</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>浏览器打开提示地址，检查：样式&#x2F;封面&#x2F;头像&#x2F;Live2D&#x2F;文章目录是否正常。</p><h2 id="3-部署到-GitHub-Pages"><a href="#3-部署到-GitHub-Pages" class="headerlink" title="3. 部署到 GitHub Pages"></a>3. 部署到 GitHub Pages</h2><p>确保 <code>_config.yml</code> 的 <code>deploy.repo</code> 指向你的 Pages 仓库（我的是 <code>https://github.com/tan1-Z/tan1.github.io.git</code>，分支 <code>gh-pages</code>）。</p><p>部署命令（需能访问 GitHub）：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pnpm run deploy   <span class="comment"># 等价 hexo deploy</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果网络受限，先配置代理环境变量再部署，例如：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 替换为你的代理端口</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$env</span>:http_proxy=<span class="string">&quot;http://127.0.0.1:7890&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="variable">$env</span>:https_proxy=<span class="string">&quot;http://127.0.0.1:7890&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">pnpm run deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="4-常见问题排查"><a href="#4-常见问题排查" class="headerlink" title="4. 常见问题排查"></a>4. 常见问题排查</h2><ul><li><code>Cannot GET /</code>：通常是 <code>source/_posts</code> 为空或生成失败。<code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g</code> 后再看 <code>public/index.html</code> 是否存在。</li><li>端口被占用：<code>hexo server -p 4002</code> 换个端口。</li><li>部署失败 <code>Failed to connect to github.com</code>：检查网络&#x2F;代理；确认 <code>deploy.repo</code> 写对；必要时重试。</li><li>头像&#x2F;封面不更新：改完 <code>_config.butterfly.yml</code> 后一定 <code>hexo clean &amp;&amp; hexo g</code>，浏览器强制刷新或清缓存。</li></ul><h2 id="5-常用命令清单"><a href="#5-常用命令清单" class="headerlink" title="5. 常用命令清单"></a>5. 常用命令清单</h2><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 新建文章</span></span><br><span class="line">hexo new <span class="string">&quot;Title&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 清理 &amp; 生成</span></span><br><span class="line">pnpm run clean</span><br><span class="line">pnpm run build        <span class="comment"># 或 hexo generate</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 本地预览</span></span><br><span class="line">pnpm <span class="built_in">exec</span> hexo server -p 4002</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 部署到 GitHub Pages</span></span><br><span class="line">pnpm run deploy       <span class="comment"># 需要网络通畅</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
      
      
